-- Maruzen Petrochemical Resumes Operations at Chiba Ethylene Plant
-- B y   J a c o b   A d e l m a n
-- 2012-06-21T06:47:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-21/maruzen-petrochemical-resumes-operations-at-chiba-ethylene-plant.html
Maruzen Petrochemical Co. started
its 525,000 metric-ton-a-year ethylene plant in Chiba near  Tokyo 
today after scheduled maintenance that began May 9, Katsuma
Shimizu, a company spokesman, said by phone from Tokyo.  To contact the reporter on this story:
